name: Alibaba Group Holding Limited
overview: Alibaba Group Holding Limited, through its subsidiaries, engages in developing consumer e-commerce, online payment, business-to-business marketplaces, and cloud computing businesses in China and internationally. It operates Alibaba.com International, an e-commerce platform for small businesses worldwide; Alibaba.com China, an e-commerce business-to-business marketplace for small businesses engaged in Chinese domestic trade; Taobao Marketplace, a consumer-to-consumer online marketplace; and AliCloud Search, a search engine that enables search for Web pages, news, pictures, and maps.
